column5: I'm thinking of signing up myself, but beating the 40 pound king Simon Barth slayed for the grand prize isn't going to be easy....PEACEOUT!
Kind of late, no? It's $100! I registered when it started, Not sure i will do it again, Just didn't get out much.

your to late bud wait till next year as far as the big fish during the derby yeah probably going to be hard to knock off but not impossible they are out there once the run is on you should have no problem bettering that fish mind you the derby will be over by then but it is still a blast
We got a couple close to 40 in an eastern trib on tuesday. Those still can be entered right?
I don't think it can be entered cause when I checked rivers like the Credit they were limited to only the first small section, but good on those king tho.....
WOW, those are huge hens for an eastern trib in Mid Aug.  Please tell me you got pics of those pigs, love to see'm!
